Vision and Core Beliefs
Your Partner To Financial Success











Superior, Cost-Effective, Unbiased Financial Planning and Investment Advice



The Vision for NCM was developed over Nick’s extensive career in the financial services industry. During this time, Nick came to realize that he wanted to serve his clients in a different way. Nick wanted to create a business model that encompassed his core beliefs:
“To build long-term relationships by offering superior, cost-effective and unbiased financial planning and investment advice, while providing outstanding personal attention and service at all times.”
It is through these efforts that NCM will achieve its goal of improving the quality of our clients' lives. 



NCM’s Core Elements to Financial Planning Success:

TRUSTWe are a fiduciary to every client, placing client interests above all else.INDEPENDENCEOnly an independent company can be truly "product neutral" and unbiased.



CLIENT UNIQUENESSAs a boutique firm, we are able to personalize financial plans and customize advice for each client’s own unique situation.FEE-ONLYClients are charged by the amount of assets, NOT by a commission for every transaction; NCM’s interests are completely aligned with those of the client.


 
 
 
 
 
 







