Bizspace Spotlight
        





 Sponsor Listing 



                    Property Spotlight: WestChase III                




See All Bizspace Properties



 







 



    Name of Partners: Maceo Sloan       Address: 2634 Durham Chapel Hill Blvd., Suite 206, Durham, N.C. 27707       Web site: www.ncmcapital.com ? Phone: (919) 688-0620  





  BUSINESS




 


    How much money does your firm have under management? We have approximately $2.3 billion.       What is your specialty/niche? Our specialty is U.S. equity and fixed income management.       How long have you been in business? We have been in business for 19 years.       Do you offer mutual funds? No, we do not offer mutual funds at this time.       Do you focus on clients in a particular class? (retirees, doctors, etc.) Our focus is on institutional investors.       How do you find clients? We find clients through referrals and utilizing the consultant community.       What's the minimum investment a client can make? The minimum investment size is $10 million.       Do you take clients looking for a quick return or do you focus on long-term strategies? We focus on long-term strategies.       How large do you want to grow your company? We would like to have 100 clients.       What's your favorite type of investment at the moment? (international, hedge, etc.) Currently, my favorite asset class is mid-cap stocks.       What's your average return on investment in the past year; in the past five years? Our 1-year return as of 6/30/05 is 15.8% and 22.6% for 5 years.  
  PERSONAL
    How long have you been in the money management business? 30 years       What personality characteristic has most helped you succeed in this business? Persistence.       What is your least favorite part of the money management business? Travel.       What are your favorite downtime activities? Golf, reading       What is your favorite vacation activity? Family travel       Family : Married, three children  







 






